and attacked me,

180
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:32,239
all but two, who stood motionless.

181
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:36,439
My guess is that one of those two
must have been my mother.

182
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:42,319
