1112
01:34:42,920 --> 01:34:44,839
(EXHALES HEAVILY)

1113
01:34:48,000 --> 01:34:51,079
(GASPING)
Just think, that when someone goes blind

1114
01:34:52,240 --> 01:34:54,100
one of the other senses

1115
