1165
01:38:31,120 --> 01:38:33,679
<i>♪ As she stared in my eyes and smiled</i>

1166
01:38:34,520 --> 01:38:37,199
<i>♪ And her lips were the colour of roses</i>

1167
01:38:38,240 --> 01:38:41,318
<i>♪ That grew down the river
all bloody and wild</i>

1168
01:38:45,880 --> 01:38:48,380
Do you like berries?
Blueberries, blackberries?

