but you know we can't do that any more.

1194
01:40:24,680 --> 01:40:27,700
Would you like to play another round of
Touch-Guess-Think-Win?

1195
01:40:27,800 --> 01:40:29,719
No, that's enough for today.

1196
01:40:31,760 --> 01:40:34,340
In any case, I've run out of things
to test you with.

1197
01:40:34,440 --> 01:40:35,620
Oh.

1198
01:40:35,720 --> 01:40:37,580
Maybe tomorrow

1199
01:40:37,680 --> 01:40:39,860
or one of these days.

1200
01:40:39,960 --> 01:40:41,940
Tomorrow morning?

1201
01:40:42,040 --> 01:40:43,639
We'll see.

1202
01:40:47,800 --> 01:40:49,519
- Bye.
- Bye.

