1230
01:43:30,240 --> 01:43:32,159
(DOGS APPROACHING)

1231
01:43:33,320 --> 01:43:34,879
(DOGS PANTING)

1232
01:43:37,600 --> 01:43:39,119
(BARKING)

1233
01:44:30,480 --> 01:44:32,399
We should speed up a little.

1234
01:44:36,160 --> 01:44:38,020
